                        "id": "Saya berasal dari Lombok.",
                        "en": "I come from Lombok."
                    }
                ],
                "grammar": {
                    "title": "Prefix Ber-",
                    "explanation": "The prefix **ber-** usually shows that a word is a verb (intransitive, no object). It often means 'to have' something or 'to be' something.",
